# migrated from tests/cases/agent_branch.it.chat (gen346, hermetic + isolated)
[mock hermetic]
!set PARROT0_BASE=
!set PARROT0_SESSION=
!set PARROT0_WORLD_FACTS=0
!set PARROT0_LANG=en
!reset

[test agent_branch.it]
# gen117 (rung 19, deeper) — bilingual ratchet for the observation-driven
# branching act-loop. The SAME code path (detect a parity condition -> parse each
# branch's operations -> observe parity each step -> apply the chosen branch ->
# repeat to the goal) runs from an Italian instruction. The competence lives in
# the algorithm: parity markers (pari/dispari), branch operations (dimezza,
# triplica, aggiungi) and the goal (finché raggiunge) are Italian; the loop and
# its canonical English report are unchanged.

# Collatz from 6 in Italian: same 8-step trajectory as the English held-out case.
> parti da 6. se è pari, dimezza. se è dispari, triplica e aggiungi 1. ripeti finché raggiunge 1.
< Reached 1 after 8 steps: 6 -> 3 -> 10 -> 5 -> 16 -> 8 -> 4 -> 2 -> 1.
